t: "And they swear by God with their strong oaths, that if a sign comes to them they will definitely believe in it. Say, \"Signs are only with God.\" And what will make you realize that (even) when the (sign) comes, they will not believe. elieve in it. Say, \"Signs are only with God.\" And what will make you realize that (even) when the (sign) comes, they will not believe"